comment: Amber did not donate the 7million dollars.  She kept it.  She blatantly lied.  She lied again about the abuse she supposedly suffered, when she was the one doing the abusing.  Then after lying about being abused, witnesses said she wore makeup bruises for her absurd press conference.  Personally, I know of no 'actually' abused  woman who would ever even think of going public in a freakin' press conference for the entire world to see.  They'd recoil from the very idea.  This woman has earned a spectacular downfall, equally as public.  She has been vicious, vindictive, gross (the poop caper), violent, self-entitled and disgusting. I am boycotting any film or tv appearance she's in.  I get too dang angry.  Although we've never met, I'm a distant cousin of Johnny's and I know what a good man he truly is through family discussions. He hasn't deserved a single bit of what she put him through.
